(47, 'Milestone  added- Not displaying  - even though visible in Edit Task', NULL, 4, 82, 15, '<p>Milestone &nbsp;added- Not displaying &nbsp;- even though visible in Edit Task</p>\r\n', '<p>Milestone &nbsp;added- Not displaying &nbsp;- even though visible in Edit Task</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Milestone added is not displayed in Assigned To others, even though it visible in Edit Task.</p>\r\n', '', '55', '', 1, 1, '2021-04-14', '2021-04-14', '2', '2021-04-14', 0, 52, '2021-04-14 15:51:06', ''),
