(51, 'Duplicates - Add New Requirements - Complexity-Priority -Status', NULL, 4, 82, 15, '<p>Duplicates - Add New Requirements - Complexity-Priority -Status</p>\r\n', '<p>Duplicates - Add New Requirements - Complexity-Priority -Status</p>\r\n', '', '<p>When adding a new requirement in requirements tab, duplicates values are visible in the drop&nbsp;down list of - Complexity- Priority and Status</p>\r\n', '', '55', '', 1, 1, '2021-04-14', '2021-04-14', '2', '2021-04-14', 0, 52, '2021-04-14 16:14:16', ''),
