(182, 'Building Installer Packages (.msi Installer Packages)', NULL, 3, 69, 17, '<p>Building Installer Packages (.msi Installer Packages) on Windows and Unix / Linux machines.</p>\r\n', '<p>Building Installer Packages (.msi Installer Packages) on Windows and Unix / Linux machines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Understand how to build .msi packages, tools to be used:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Blade Logic for Windows.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ansible for Unix / Linux machines.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please do a research and understand the working functionality to do .msi packages, i am attaching some quick links i found on google, and summarized basic information in a PPT attached (as we had same on screen share).</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Building Installer Packages (.msi Installer Packages) on Windows and Unix / Linux machines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Understand how to build .msi packages, tools to be used:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Blade Logic for Windows.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ansible for Unix / Linux machines.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What Is An .MSI File?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A typical MSI file is a database that may contain the following elements:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;User Interface to install the files</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Executable (.exe) files</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Open Database Connectivity Settings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Configuration settings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Registry settings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Custom actions to be executed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Installation instructions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Order of installation procedure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Actual file to be installed, or the path for the uncompressed file location</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;Other relevant files</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;All this information is necessary to install the associated application properly on a desktop or server.</p>\r\n', '', '42', '', 1, 1, '2021-05-26', '2021-05-31', '32', '2021-05-26', 0, 52, '2021-05-26 16:04:31', 'dinesh@digitowork.com,Krishnaprasad@digitowork.com'),
(183, 'Attachment added in tasks are not displayed', NULL, 4, 70, 15, '<p>Attachment added in tasks are not displayed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uploaded attachments in tasks are not visible on editing tasks.</p>\r\n', '<p>Attachment added in tasks are not displayed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Uploaded attachments in tasks are not visible on editing tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Also, uploaded files are not being sent to the receipants in the emails.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Attachment added in tasks are not displayed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Uploaded attachments in tasks are not visible on editing tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Also, uploaded files are not being sent to the receipants in the emails.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Add a new task and upload the files.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. On editing the task, the uploaded file is not visible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Also the attachments are not sent in the emails.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '55,52', '', 1, 1, '2021-05-26', '2021-05-29', '6', '2021-05-26', 0, 52, '2021-05-26 16:20:42', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
