(185, 'Implement MFA with Open Source Software', NULL, 3, 78, 12, '<p>Implement MFA (Multi-Factor Authentication) with Open Source Software on the Server.</p>\r\n', '<p>Implement MFA (Multi-Factor Authentication) with Open Source Software on the Server.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search for open source softwares which allows for implementation of MFA, which we can implement on our server. (Document the procedure and steps).</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Implement MFA (Multi-Factor Authentication) with Open Source Software on the Server.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search for open source softwares which allows for implementation of MFA.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A code should be sent for example to email and should be verified for login authentication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please refer a link that might help:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://auth0.com/blog/different-ways-to-implement-multifactor/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '42', '', 1, 1, '2021-06-08', '2021-06-10', '8', '2021-06-08', 0, 52, '2021-06-08 10:50:41', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
