(240, 'VA - Software Cobol Applications', NULL, 5, 81, 16, '<p>Understanding and researching on&nbsp;Security Vulnerability Scanning Software for Cobol Applications</p>\r\n', '<p>Understanding and researching on&nbsp;Security Vulnerability Scanning Software for Cobol Applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The primary goal is the ability for the tool to perform application security testing (AST) on source code written in various versions of the COBOL programming language, both inside and outside the Continuous Integration / Continuous Delivery (CI/CD) DevOps pipeline.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Understanding the researching on&nbsp;Security Vulnerability Scanning Software for Cobol Applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please refer the technical capabilities in the attached RFI dcoument and research accordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prepare a report on your findings of research and gather a summary of the same.</p>\r\n', '', '42', '', 1, 1, '2021-06-19', '2021-06-22', '16', '2021-06-19', 0, 52, '2021-06-19 13:11:02', 'dinesh@digitowork.com,Krishnaprasad@digitowork.com'),
