(248, 'Add Done% column to Task Status:', NULL, 4, 82, 15, '<p>Add Done% column to Task Status:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Goal is to add Done% Column to Task Status and display details correctly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In View Task for assigned tasks, add Done% column to Task Status-Whenever Done% or Status is changed, the change history to be displayed accordingly for Done%, example: on 5th date Done % is 40 and on 10th date Done % is 70, it should be displayed accordingly with corresponding details and Done%.</p>\r\n', '<p>Add Done% column to Task Status:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In View Task for assigned tasks, add Done% column to Task Status-Whenever Done% or Status is changed, the change history to be displayed accordingly for Done%, example: on 5th date Done % is 40 and on 10th date Done % is 70, it should be displayed accordingly with corresponding details and Done%.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Add Done% column to Task Status:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In View Task for assigned tasks, add Done% column to Task Status-Whenever Done% or Status is changed, the change history to be displayed accordingly for Done%, example: on 5th date Done % is 40 and on 10th date Done % is 70, it should be displayed accordingly with corresponding details and Done%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The column Done% to added and displayed at the bottom i.e. in Task Status</p>\r\n', '', '55', '', 2, 1, '2021-06-22', '2021-06-25', '16', '2021-06-22', 0, 52, '2021-06-22 12:18:44', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
(249, 'Display Audit Trails - Add change history', NULL, 4, 82, 15, '<p>Display Audit Trails - Add change history</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Goal is adding change history in the form of Audit Trail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>(Since Done% not working) &amp; change history not displayed.)</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>Display Audit Trails - Add change history in Task Status</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In View Task for assigned tasks, add audit trails i.e. whenever status is changed or Done% is updated, the status, updated by and Date&amp;Time details should be displayed in the form of Change History as an Audit Trail. For example Status is InProgress but Done% is changed from 20% to 45%, the change history should be displayed with details such as who updated it and Done% details.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Display Audit Trails - Add change history in Task Status</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In View Task for assigned tasks, add audit trails i.e. whenever status is changed or Done% is updated, the status, updated by and Date&amp;Time details should be displayed in the form of Change History as an Audit Trail. For example Status is InProgress but Done% is changed from 20% to 45%, the change history should be displayed with details such as who updated it and Done% details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Task Status should display change history - Audit Trail.</p>\r\n', '', '55', '248', 2, 1, '2021-06-22', '2021-06-26', '16', '2021-06-22', 0, 52, '2021-06-22 12:23:58', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
