(270, 'Remind me on (Date) – Functionality:', NULL, 4, 82, 15, '<p>Goal is to set a &quot;Remind me&nbsp;on&quot; (Date) &ndash; Functionality:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>(Alert not disappearing on completion of task)</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>Steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A new task is added by the supervisor and it gets added to My To-Do List.</li>\r\n	<li>For the newly added task in the My-To-Do List, we shall have a feature for&nbsp;each individual tasks in My-To-Do List that a user can Edit Task and set a reminder as &ldquo;<strong>Remind me on</strong>&rdquo; as in the screen shot attached.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', '<p>Steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A new task is added by the supervisor and it gets added to My To-Do List.</li>\r\n	<li>For the newly added task in the My-To-Do List, we shall have a feature for&nbsp;each individual tasks in My-To-Do List that a user can Edit Task and set a reminder as &ldquo;<strong>Remind me on</strong>&rdquo; as in the screen shot attached.</li>\r\n	<li>Note: this reminder will be set by the person working on the task.</li>\r\n	<li>A pop-up should be displayed with the list of reminders set when we click on the bell icon the top pane of the application. Also, the bell icon should show the number of reminders</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', '55', '', 2, 1, '2021-07-12', '2021-07-17', '8', '2021-07-12', 0, 52, '2021-07-12 06:26:11', 'dinesh@digitowork.com,Krishnaprasad@digitowork.com'),
