(502, 'Assets Assignment- Email Trigger', NULL, 8, 86, 20, '<p>Email Should Trigger when an asset will be assigned to the user.</p>\r\n', '<p>When Asset will be assigned to the user, an email should trigger and it will go to the assigned user and Manager (Supervisor).</p>\r\n', '', '<p><strong>Steps:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Create an Alert for For Mail Trigger.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Set Condition on which condition it will trigger.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Filter the record by which column, the condition will satisfy.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Select who will be the&nbsp;recipients.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Select Recipients Details.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Select Workflow Templates.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Publish.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '57', '', 1, 2, '2022-01-24', '2022-01-24', '5', '2022-01-24', 0, 57, '2022-01-24 05:18:49', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
