(504, 'Trigger Mail When Data Is Different', NULL, 8, 85, 2, '<p><strong>If Catalog Data is different than asset catalog data, which is associated with the same catalog then email should trigger to the end-user and the manager.</strong></p>\r\n', '', '', '<p><strong>Steps:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Create a Catalog with sufficient&nbsp;Data.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Create an Asset with the same catalog (Derived Assets).</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Make Sure all catalog essential data should come into Asset Page.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Save &amp; Close Asset Form.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Change Memory Column Data from Asset Form.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Based on catalog Data change from Asset Form Email should Trigger.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Email Should go to the End- User and Manager (Supervisor).</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Above all are conditions which we have to apply and create an alert.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '57', '', 1, 2, '2022-01-24', '2022-01-24', '5', '2022-01-24', 0, 57, '2022-01-24 06:55:10', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
