(506, 'Compare Discovery and Lifecycle Data', NULL, 8, 86, 20, '<p><strong>If the Assets serial number and Discovery serial number are the same but any data differ from Lifecycle and Discovery then We need a complete report of both (Lifecycle and Discovery). Email should also trigger.</strong></p>\r\n', '', '', '<p><strong>Steps:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Take One Catalog and Associate Asset Data with Same Catalog (Derived Asset).</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Check Discovery Data.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Compare All the Data of Discovery and Lifecycle.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Export All Data of Lifecycle and Discovery Data.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. If Data is Differ in Discovery&nbsp;from Lifecycle Email Should Trigger.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '57', '', 1, 1, '2022-01-25', '2022-01-25', '5', '2022-01-25', 0, 57, '2022-01-25 10:53:01', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
