(591, 'Assigned to list', NULL, 4, 70, 14, '<p>The &quot;Assigned to&quot; list for the Project ITAM-GASOC does not show Dinesh&#39;s name. But he is also part of the Project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>His name should also be listed as he is part of the Project.</p>\r\n', '<p>The &quot;Assigned to&quot; list for the Project ITAM-GASOC does not show Dinesh&#39;s name. But he is also part of the Project.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Go to ITAM-GASOC project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check the list of employees when assigning the task.</p>\r\n', '', '55', '', 2, 1, '2022-03-29', '2022-03-29', '4', '2022-03-29', 0, 61, '2022-03-29 08:41:56', 'dinesh@digitowork.com'),
