(30, 0, 32, 'Assets Location ', 'Assets Location', 0, '<p>Assets Location is not same for the employee&#39;s location for whom the asset was assigned.</p>\r\n', '2019-12-09 16:35:42', NULL, '2021-03-08 10:47:52', 0, 1),
(31, 0, 33, 'Inserting a pdf in the csv', 'CG', 0, '<p>When pdf is inserted in the excel the file format is will be xlt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>when xlt is saved ad CSV there will be a warning saying there may be loss of data in conversion to CSV format.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Though it is saved. The pdf is not available in the CSV file.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CSV only takes singular text with the respective delimited. The pdf cannot be inserted in the CSV as pdf is not a singular text.</p>\r\n', '2019-12-24 19:20:00', NULL, '2021-03-08 10:47:47', 0, 1),
(32, 0, 38, 'Vendor-Company-Supplier', '', 4, '<p>Vendor and Supplier&nbsp;are the same in eracent</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-12-26 16:43:13', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(33, 0, 38, 'Supplier-Company', '', 4, '<p>Companies and Suppliers are not same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make and Supplier(Vendor) are differnt but they both are taking the values from the same table . Need to add seperate table of values&nbsp;for Make</p>\r\n', '2019-12-26 18:43:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(34, 0, 38, 'Relationship between Make,Vendor,Purchased from,Supplier', '', 4, '<p>The following fields sounds different in different Modules but the functionality is same and the table of data is also same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Module&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Contact, PO, Catalog, Asset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Field&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :Vendor, Purchased from, Make(Supplier), Make</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TableName&nbsp; :Select Contracts Vendor, Company, Companies, _</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FieldName&nbsp; &nbsp;:CompanyName,&nbsp;CompanyName,&nbsp;CompanyName, _</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2019-12-27 11:01:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 2),
(35, 0, 40, 'Vendor Types, companies', '', 4, '<p>The following fields sounds different in different Modules but the functionality is same and the table of data is also same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Module&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Contact, PO, Catalog, Asset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Field&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Vendor, Purchased from, Make(Supplier), Make</p>\r\n\r\n<p>please refer the document for more clarification.</p>\r\n', '2019-12-27 14:53:36', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
