(298, 266, 42, '<p><strong>TOOLS FOR THREAT INTELLIGENCE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Anomali Threat stream:</strong><br />\r\nSecurity teams can identify hidden threats targeting thier environments<br />\r\nHarness threat data, information and intelligence to make effective cyber security decisions<br />\r\nProvides tools and researches for free<br />\r\n<tt>https://www.anomali.com/products/threatstream</tt></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AT &amp; T Cybersecurity:</strong><br />\r\nAlienVault Unified Security Management (USM), a product of AT&amp;T CyberSecurity, receives threat intelligence from AlienVault Labs and its massive Open Threat Exchange (OTX), the world&rsquo;s largest crowd-sourced collaborative threat exchange. It provides centralized threat detection, incident response and compliance management for cloud and on-premises environments.<br />\r\n<tt>https://cybersecurity.att.com/</tt></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recorded future threat intelligence</strong><br />\r\nRecording data about who is attacking them and what their motivations and capabilities are, and what indicators of compromise in your systems to look for - that helps you make informed decisions about your security.<br />\r\n<tt>https://www.recordedfuture.com/solutions/threat-intelligence/</tt></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Here is the useful link comprising about different tools and their descriptions:</strong><br />\r\n<span class=\"marker\"><tt>https://www.esecurityplanet.com/products/threat-intelligence-platforms/</tt></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '2021-07-01', '2021-07-01', 1, '', 'Y', 0, '2021-07-02 21:38:28', '0000-00-00', '', '', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N'),
