(301, 269, 42, '<p>Here&#39;s the Data that I&#39;ve gained completing the&nbsp;CTF: (The Points mentioned to be chased for completing CTF)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Analysis Filename:</strong>&nbsp;attack.pcapng</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tool to be used:</strong>&nbsp;WireShark<br />\r\n<strong>User name:</strong>&nbsp;coffee<br />\r\n<strong>Source:</strong>192.168.0.10<br />\r\n<strong>Destination:</strong>&nbsp;192.168.0.28<br />\r\n<strong>Password:</strong>&nbsp;P@$$W0RD@123#$<br />\r\n<strong>File transferred:</strong>&nbsp;file.txt<br />\r\n<strong>and<br />\r\nTHE FINAL PASSPHRASE:</strong><br />\r\nCTF{7H!$I$N07H!1n9}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Applications Used:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Base64 Decode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>WireShark</em></p>\r\n', '<p>-</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Using Wireshark to view the captured packets</li>\r\n	<li>Viewing file&#39;s data in Wireshark</li>\r\n	<li>Decoding Base64 encrypted data</li>\r\n	<li>Getting files from the host webserver</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '2021-07-13', '2021-07-13', 1, '', 'Y', 0, '2021-07-13 00:36:57', '0000-00-00', '', '', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N'),
