(321, 289, 42, '<p><strong>BitNetSentry</strong>: Embedded Systems&nbsp;developed a combined hardware and software product line called BitNetSentry (BNS), that secures organizations from various cyber-attacks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the Key points of BIT NET SENTRY PRODUCT:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. BNS ensures that critical and sensitive Information will not: leak out, get breached, get stolen, change without authorization or maliciously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. BNS secures from MITM (Man-In-The-Middle attack), authorized supply chain, and also Insiders. Even when attackers have IT privileges and encryption keys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. BNS ensures bit-level security (Data Link Layer).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. BNS is Invisible in the network (no MAC nor IP address).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. BNS is utilizing &lsquo;Encryption without encryption&rsquo; in addition to legacy encryptions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Please find the attached PDF file for the complete synopsis report on BNS.</p>\r\n', '<p>-</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Overview of BIT NET SENTRY and its influence in IT Security.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '2021-07-22', '2021-07-22', 1, '4', 'Y', 0, '2021-07-22 09:47:09', '0000-00-00', '', '', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N'),
