(502, 468, 57, '<p><strong>Batch Update Process:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>We can perform batch update in Catalog, Assets and Contracts.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>For Performing Batch update in Catalog Navigate this:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifecycle &gt;&nbsp;Catalog &gt;&nbsp;Tasks &gt;&nbsp;Batch Update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>For Performing Batch update in Assets Navigate this:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifecycle &gt; Assets &gt; Asset Management &gt; Asset Tasks &gt; Batch Update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>For Performing Batch update in Contracts Navigate this:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Lifecycle &gt; Contracts &amp; Procurement &gt; Tasks &gt; Contracts Batch Update</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Performing Batch update in Catalog:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>To perform a batch update of existing catalog items, go to the Lifecycle section and click <strong>Catalog</strong> &gt; <strong>Tasks</strong> &gt; <strong>Batch Update</strong> in the menu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First search for <strong>Catalog Items</strong> you wish to perform <strong>Batch Update</strong> using query located on the bottom of the page. Select checkboxes of <strong>Catalog Items</strong> to be updated and move to the top of the page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In <strong>Batch Update</strong> for <strong>Catalog Items</strong> section select <strong>Catalog Item</strong> attributes to be updated that will allow you to enter values in relevant fields that will get updated while performing <strong>Batch Update</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You may also use buttons placed on the top of the section:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;<strong>Select All</strong>&quot; to select all attributes,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;<strong>Select None</strong>&quot; to remove previously selected attributes or</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;<strong>Invert Selection</strong>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When all the values that needs to be changed are entered press &quot;Perform Batch Update&quot; button to run the update or &quot;Cancel&quot; to discard changes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Alert: -</strong> <strong>If the box is checked the value will propagate to the asset level. WARNING: Propagating may override existing values at the asset level.</strong></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '2021-12-28', '2021-12-28', 1, '5', 'N', 0, '2022-01-10 05:45:16', '1970-01-01', '28', '', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N');
